Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,PERFORMANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Hey, I thought we were supposed\Nto be meeting every other week,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,not this often.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] It can't be helped.\NWe just received a new report from Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that Misa Amane might know L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Coil, L once questioned\NAmane as part of his Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But see, here's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, "I've been able to deduce\Nthat Amane worships Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, Yoshida Productions\Nis trying to promote Amane
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as the new face of Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My recommendation is that Yotsuba use her\Nfor the next ad campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and take the opportunity\Nto extract information about L."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I don't like the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unacceptable, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?\NIt seems like a perfectly good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] I don't think that's\Nwhat Ooi was trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be Coil's job\Nto investigate L's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense for him to leave\Nall the hard work to us, in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. We're paying him\Nto uncover L's identity, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we contact Coil\Nand see what he has to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] Yes, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kida, I thought we agreed before\Nthat you'd only call me if it was urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I think I have\Nan even better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Even after\Nthose meetings are over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to come home to punish criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Being Kira is so time-consuming,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but things sure have become\Nmore interesting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty clear that Misa Amane\Nis the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and that L must have\Ncaught her at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way she could have\Ngotten out of that situation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is by forfeiting ownership\Nof her Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and losing all memories\Nof what she did with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not about to leave things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make Misa Amane my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I could ever want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, power, and a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be enough to make anyone envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're married, I'll just invest\Na large lump sum in her life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] She would never marry\Nsuch a disgusting fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, make sure you hide the notebook\Nin the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, this is the only thing I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,for Misa's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] All right!\NLet's try again, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true you once said that you came\Nto Tokyo in order to meet Ki--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-[L groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, please stop overacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks too cheesy, not to mention fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I thought\Nthat was a realistic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Just do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, oh, so great director...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If you don't get serious about this,\NI'll kick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa harrumphs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Misa-Misa…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not smiling enough, Mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can just call me Misa, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cut out for this,\Nbut it's part of my job so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales dramatically]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Misa-Misa!\N-What is it, Mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you have an interview\Nwith the Yotsuba Group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if they'll use you\Nin their new ad campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember,\Nthis is also an infiltration mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so stay sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.\NI already know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, that means\Nyou can't let your cover fall either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna play the character\Nof the hyper-energetic manager, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Right! Bring it on!\N[cheers]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shimura] Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Misa-Misa's manager, Kanichi Moji,\Nalso known as Mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Ooi, Mr. Shimura.\N-Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Way to go, Mochi. You're a natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here ready to celebrate\Nwhen they decide to hire you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I don't believe\Nyou and I have met before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have we, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is John Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the executive adviser\Nfor the advertising department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nice to meet you.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this might seem a little bit sudden\Nbut I'd like to be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been talking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've pretty much decided\Nto hire you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But before we make it official,\Nwe'd like to clarify a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been doing\Na little background check on you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and according to our sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a burglar killed your parents\Nduring a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You worship Kira\Nbecause he killed the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that you came to Tokyo\Nin hope of finding and meeting Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aiber] I'm afraid I can't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The information is reliable, and now,\NI'd say it's confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The look on your face tells me\Nthat these are the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] Coil, I never thought\Nyou investigated that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you're still hiding something\Nfrom us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you'd prefer\Nthe world not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's where I pause\Nand look nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you were detained\Nby the detective L
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to tell us the full story\Nof what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a problem if the new face\Nof Yotsuba turned out to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We would appreciate it\Nif you were honest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Yes, I was held for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it was L,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but he did ask me lots of questions\Nabout Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the second Kira,\Nand I never was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was released because he realized
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have anything to do\Nwith Kira after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you manage to see who it was\Nthat was restraining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] No, I was blindfolded\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he asked you questions,\Nsurely you heard his voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Only through a speaker\Nand voice filters, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A job interview or a police interrogation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are we gonna keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a point. It seems the interview\Nveered a little off track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but would you mind\Nif I went to the bathroom as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[water flowing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Oh, this is getting exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything's going well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Being touched by this scrap of paper alone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will not restore her memories\Nof the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least now,\NMisa can see me once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa whimpers] What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, you're in a dangerous situation\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people within Yotsuba\Nwho can easily have you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come here to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Calm down? How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing looks like it's gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, believe me, I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My… ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Oh man,\NI wonder if Misa-Misa's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have wired her\Nor used something to track her movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kira before I was detained\Nand the one that surfaced afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they must be two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The MO clearly doesn't match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This Kira is killing criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as they've had\Ntheir crime broadcast on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's punishing people\Nwho never intended to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,those who sincerely regretted\Ntheir crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or people with excusable circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The original Kira would have\Nnever punished those kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sort of distinction I'd make,\Nif I were him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the original Kira acted\Nis disturbingly close to my ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] What the hell am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's gotta be wrong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm seriously comparing myself\Nto that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what is Light doing\Nat the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled speech]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can tell you're not a stalker,\Nbut you don't look like a human at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you were captured by L,\Nyou and I worked closely together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me? And Light is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It grants its owner the power\Nto kill someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,simply by writing\Nthat person's name in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami took it upon himself\Nto punish criminals using that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He soon became known to the world\Nas Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You also possess that same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, your ability\Nwas even greater than his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to find Light
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,by using your power to determine\Nthat he was, in fact, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is Kira, and I'm the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] That's right.\NOr rather, that used to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Light arranged it so you would both\Nlose this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all according to his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He did? Then Ryuzaki was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, do you still love Light\Nenough to die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally believe you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And, yes, I do love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention how amazing it is\Nthat Light and I were both Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd want to believe\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish I could remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems your feelings for Light\Nwill never change either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough to convince me\Nthat the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be truly happy in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is if you can support him in his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you, Shinigami.\N-It's Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Kira is a vile\Nand pathetic human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, and beware the others\Nfrom Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Trust Light. Let him do\Nwhatever he feels necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should just act normal\Nin the meantime, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go back to the interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be able to see for yourself\Nwho the real Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on your guard and do not trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, I'm so sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just fixing up my makeup a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Listen, when you return,\NI will be in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The man sitting in front of me\Nwill be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] The person in front of you is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Higuchi is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Misa-Misa sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opening]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey...\N-How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba agreed to hire Misa on\Nas their spokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for their new ad campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I see. That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I made sure to give them\Nmy cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you believe three out of seven guys\Nalready messaged me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,asking for a private date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I accept their invitations\Nand investigate them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's going exactly as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] No, the plan's\Ngetting canceled right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's been going so smoothly\Nup until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go any further, you'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still appear in their commercials\Nbut from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you should deny that you were suspected\Nof being the second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and was detained by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi will continue being your bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll be working solely\Nas a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] If that's what you want, Light,\Nthen that's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'm feeling pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's shoot is bright and early,\Nso I better get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Light. You're so sweet\Nto be worried about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've thought of the best plan ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be useful to you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Hey, Light, want to come\Nsleep with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saving it\Nfor after we catch Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be shy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Light, there's no need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No need to be so serious either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[director] Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay, that's a wrap!\N-Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Great job, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mochi. Can you take me\Nto the restroom in that hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TO-OH WOMEN'S MEDICAL CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure not to take too long, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nori] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa! You actually made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nori, you look so cute\Nin that nurse's outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles] You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,TO-OH WOMEN'S MEDICAL CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like it,\NI'll give you a ride anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or buy you one of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nloving that nurse's outfit, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa giggles] I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] That took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mogi exclaims]\N-[nervous laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's Misa?\N-She's on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke Higuchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The sleazy pervert who's been sending me\Ntext messages ever since that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been even more persistent\Nthan any of the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't get any worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Misa?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we grab a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to take me somewhere\Nand do pervy things to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if you are, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, since I can kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this part of Light Yagami's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what he wants you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this your way of telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that you want me to kill Higuchi\Nthe moment he tries to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're just kidding with me,\Naren't you, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's true. And you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she was the second Kira before,\Nthere's no way she still is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not supposed to have\Nany memory of it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi laughs] Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to make up stuff like that\Nto feel safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find\Nthat I'm quite the gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa chuckles nervously] Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll only prove\Nthat I'm the second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NYou'll only show proof to Kira? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I'd show him because it's always\Nbeen my dream to become Kira's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he'll need me by his side\Nonce I tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NIf she really is the second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's pretty clear\Nfrom the Sakura TV incident
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that she has the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to make sure I keep this girl\Nby my side at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to test her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I happen to be Kira,\Ndoes that mean you'll marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then prove it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's prove it to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a pretty bad idea\Nto let someone witness how I kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NIf I thought someone was Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be willing to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never get anywhere if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]\NThen why don't you kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I could be the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right,\Nbut I only kill bad people, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A bad person, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ginzo Kaneboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,President of a major finance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's infamous\Nfor his immoral collection methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, he even makes people\Npay with their insurance money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Would you be able\Nto confirm his death right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Yeah, as soon as I call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Okay then.\NCould you turn around for just a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[scribbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, you want me to kill Ginzo Kaneboshi,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Higuchi will believe your claim\Nabout being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,GINZO KANEBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. He should be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Higuchi from Yotsuba--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Sorry, our president just collapsed\Nand stopped breathing! Call back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[man hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The same guy I chose just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Would've been impossible to do that\Nunless she had the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] So, if I'm Kira,\Nyou'll marry me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you getting so serious\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Because I'm Kira.\N-Then prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna be able to kill\Nuntil I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, that's no good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For all I know,\Nyou're just making all this up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have an excuse\Nto take me to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait! I know.\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop killing the criminals\Non TV? That should prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're Kira, it should be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start killing again\Nwhen I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If all the times and deaths match up,\Nthen I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, killing criminals in that way\Nis something that only Kira can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kira, so in order\Nto make you trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and prove that I'm him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop killing criminals\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then once you're fully convinced\NI'm the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you and I can get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, based on what he said,\NHiguchi is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we not only know Kira's identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but all those deaths that were worrying\Nthe chief are gonna stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
